{"tid":894662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧小平有改革開放;習近平都有改革","createTime":"2018-11-08T14:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T15:13:21.000Z","uid":134437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec76355b9c601e5b4bc1b748157fec38cad1f6e","tid":894662,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"廁所改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廁所皇帝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本次北京召開新世代廁所博覽會，應該順應中國國家主席習近平從2015年以來提倡的「廁所革命「潮流。<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月，習近平對中國旅遊系統的「廁所革命」表示讚揚，並指示這一革命「不是小事」，是中國城鄉文明建設的重要方面，要求景區，城市、農村都要提高廁所質量，稱這是中國民眾「生活品質的短板」。<br />\n<br />\n過去，中國廁所「髒亂差」問題，曾經在國際間「臭名遠揚」。如廁問題，一度被西方遊客認為是在中國面對的最大難題。<br />\n<br />\n習近平「廁所革命」3年來，中國各地建造了數以萬計的廁所，有的甚至成為官員貪污腐敗的工程。"},{"pid":"1fe62900f532cd2d17156a92e655287c3208a3f3","tid":894662,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"改黎做乜 都唔會入廁所屙架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2a3db84bb0030e83fc483dc5728e6f7f89529f","tid":894662,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"蓋茨打破中國「四T禁忌」 推廣廁所革命<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46110805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46110805&d=sTyggjgnhWiX9Xa0VAlZzzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3ee85035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46110805&h=5d2b0284\" target=\"_blank\">www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46110805</a>"},{"pid":"768941bbe6ae1a2388250f20335e6ce7873b227c","tid":894662,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe62900f532cd2d17156a92e655287c3208a3f3","tid":894662,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"改黎做乜 都唔會入廁所屙架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e72a48456894f559b9756c5a73cc9f7da37570","tid":894662,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"希望你唔好攞埋啲乜嘢鄧小平同千古一帝比"},{"pid":"35240ef2630c8af53b345b58d87722784b02bb49","tid":894662,"uid":32675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"明明中国人覺得普天之下,莫非糞坑,何必搞咩乾淨廁所呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8606195e8fcb669c172783a8fa26de31835b45b","tid":894662,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"鄧小平就人人有飯食<br />\n<br />\n雜種就人人有屎屙！"}]}